data.description: This Amazing  home is what you've  been searching  for. This Beautiful  home completely  renovated  in a Nice community,  fresh  interior paint,  porcelain and title flooring  throughout,  new lighting,  perfect your  culinary  creations  in the chef's  kitchen,  with  a  nice island  and breakfast bar, the private  master suite  features  a walk in closet and a spacious  bathroom. Nice  backyard  with  a covered  patio  and storage  shed.New fence , two car garage,  two driveway  entrance.   No HOA, NEVER FLOODED,  NO RESTRICTIONS.   This is a 3 bedrooms,  2 Bathrooms, Media room or playroom, Living room,  dining area, Kitchen, Office  room, laundry room.   You don't want to miss to see this incredible  home.  Call Today!
